48188.text: [48188] StaticText 'COMPACT DESIGN FOR TAILORED BIRD FEEDING'

48193.text: [48193] StaticText 'TRULY SQUIRREL-PROOF: Openings in the shroud align with the feeding ports, providing birds access to the food. When a squirrel climbs onto the feeder, its weight automatically forces the shroud down, closing access to the ports. Squirrels and some large birds are foiled but not harmed in any way'

48198.text: [48198] StaticText 'PAYS FOR ITSELF IN SAVED SEED: Squirrels can no longer steal your wild bird seed. Over a short period of time this adds up to substantial savings that will pay for the purchase of your feeder'

48203.text: [48203] StaticText 'RECOMMENDED BIRD FOOD: Black oil sunflower or/and safflower seeds'

48208.text: [48208] StaticText 'LIFETIME CARE: This is how we support you and our planet. Should you need a part covered under our warranty, we will provide it for free to extend the life of our products, and shipping is on us. The future of the planet must be linked to the vision of products made to last. Please call us for advice or help, a real person will be happy to answer'
